questions.question:
Label the program below with the following: class declaration, class name, main method, statement, opening curly bracket, closing curly bracket, semicolon.

public class Hello {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello from Java");
    }
}

questions.answer:
class declaration -> public class Hello
class name -> Hello
main method -> public static void main(String[] args)
statement -> System.out.println("Hello from Java");
opening curly bracket -> {
closing curly bracket -> }
semicolon -> ; after the println statement

